flowchart LR
    Flow[Integration Suite Flow] -->|POST run summary| API[Integration Pulse Payload API]
    API --> DB[(PostgreSQL integration_payloads)]
    DB --> Summary[Payload Summary Metadata]
    Summary --> MPL[Monitoring Row matched by messageId]
    MPL --> Preview[Preview if <= 100 KB]
    MPL --> Download[Download if downloadOnly]
    DB --> Retention[Expires after 7 days]
